summary:
According to an old Hungarian legend a tribe of the Huns migrated east, they are the Celts.
Hungarian language in the Eastern=KELET, Celtic=KELTA
Full ebony armor,weapons.Ancient Celtic,Scythian, Hun gold artifacts pictures using.
I used images of archaeological finds,I think it\'s free use.
Craftable,temperable standalone version for women,men
